Considering c_cpp_properties.json -- 
depending on your VSC setup you may want one of the following:
(1) add the following to the configuration object:
  "compileCommands": "build_vsc/compile_commands.json"
(2) add the following to the configuration object:
  "includePath": [ "${workspaceFolder}/**" ],
(3) add the following to the configuration object: 
  "configurationProvider": "vector-of-bool.cmake-tools"
